 data knowledge (pre-2025). Served as梅江区委书记 ~2016-2021, later promoted to梅州市人大常委会副主任." /></attvalues></node><node id="3" label="胡金良"><viz:size value="60.0" /><viz:shape value="square" /><viz:color r="200" g="30" b="30" a="1.0" /><attvalues><attvalue for="0" value="person" /><attvalue for="1" value="不详（可能为梅江区委书记或另有任命）" /><attvalue for="2" value="不详" /><attvalue for="3" value="男" /><attvalue for="4" value="汉族" /><attvalue for="5" value="不详" /><attvalue for="6" value="Training data knowledge (pre-2025). May have succeeded陈金銮 as区委书记, but this is uncertain and requires verification." /></attvalues></node><node id="4" label="钟秀堂"><viz:size value="50.0" /><viz:shape value="circle" /><viz:color r="30" g="100" b="200" a="1.0" /><attvalues><attvalue for="0" value="person" /><attvalue for="1" value="五华县县长（现任）" /><attvalue for="2" value="五华县人民政府" /><attvalue for="3" value="女" /><attvalue for="4" value="汉族" /><attvalue for="5" value="1974年4月" /><attvalue for="6" value="Training data knowledge (pre-2025). Served as梅江区区长, later transferred to五华县 as县长." /></attvalues></node><node id="5" label="刘东峰"><viz:size value="50.0" /><viz:shape value="circle" /><viz:color r="30" g="100" b="200" a="1.0" /><attvalues><attvalue for="0" value="person" /><attvalue for="1" value="不详（可能为梅江区区长或梅州市其他职务）" /><attvalue for="2" value="不详" /><attvalue for="3" value="男" /><attvalue for="4" value="汉族" /><attvalue for="5" value="不详" /><attvalue for="6" value="Training data knowledge (pre-2025). Possibly succeeded钟秀堂 as区长. Requires verification." /></attvalues></node><node id="6" label="王增文"><viz:size value="45.0" /><viz:shape value="square" /><viz:color r="220" g="80" b="80" a="0.9" /><attvalues><attvalue for="0" value="person" /><attvalue for="1" value="梅江区委副书记（可能任上）" /><attvalue for="2" value="中共梅州市梅江区委员会" /><attvalue for="3" value="男" /><attvalue for="4" value="汉族" /><attvalue for="5" value="不详" /><attvalue for="6" value="Training data knowledge. Requires verification." /></attvalues></node><node id="7" la